<p><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;国家安全，重于泰山，一头连着国家的前途命运，一头系着人民的幸福安康。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2025年4月15日，是第10个全民国家安全教育日，主题是“全民国家安全教育 走深走实十周年”。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744791436905.jpg" alt="1744791436905.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744791436905.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744791461737.jpg" alt="1744791461737.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744791461737.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744791482899.jpg" alt="1744791482899.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744791482899.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744791511467.jpg" alt="1744791511467.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744791511467.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744791528325.jpg" alt="1744791528325.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744791528325.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744791547653.jpg" alt="1744791547653.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744791547653.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744791571345.jpg" alt="1744791571345.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744791571345.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744791597590.jpg" alt="1744791597590.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744791597590.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744791620587.jpg" alt="1744791620587.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744791620587.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744791647190.jpg" alt="1744791647190.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744791647190.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744791695075.jpg" alt="1744791695075.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744791695075.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744791716589.jpg" alt="1744791716589.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744791716589.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744791764340.jpg" alt="1744791764340.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744791764340.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744791788282.jpg" alt="1744791788282.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744791788282.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744791810394.jpg" alt="1744791810394.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744791810394.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744791841671.jpg" alt="1744791841671.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1744791841671.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;">国家安全是民族复兴的根基</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;">社会稳定是国家强盛的前提</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;">国家安全人人有责</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;">维护国家安全人人可为</span></p>